<p>On behave of the WMC’22 Program Committee, we are glad to announce that the WMC is accepted and will officially be held together with RTSS’22 in Houston.</p>

<p>More information can be found on the <a href="http://2022.rtss.org/hot-topics-day-cfp/">RTSS’22 Hot Topics Day</a>.</p>

<p>Please consider to make a submission to WMC. You can find the call for papers <a href="/cfp/">here</a>. The submission link is also open on EasyChair, which can be accessed at: <a href="https://easychair.org/conferences/?conf=wmc2022">https://easychair.org/conferences/?conf=wmc2022</a>.</p>

<p>We are looking forward to see you on the workshop!</p>

